			
					README of HINDI_GENERATOR
					-----  -- ---------------

Requirements:
------------
Operating System                :    LINUX/UNIX system

Compiler/Interpreter/Librarie(s):    Perl and SSF API's

How to Use??
-----------

>> perl ./hindi_gen.pl --path=/home/hin_gen [-i inputfile|--input="input_file"] [-o outputfile|--output="output_file"]

   *Sample input and output files are provided in the home dir namely input.txt, output.txt 




